# macOS
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Ephemeral session state (regenerated each session)
scratchpad/manifest*.md
scratchpad/checkpoint.md

# Temp files from bin/cg-slug
/tmp/cg-slug-*

# Personal data — not tracked in the public repo
# Users: these dirs are yours. Track them in your own private fork if you want.
projects/_active/*
!projects/_active/.gitkeep
projects/_archived/*
!projects/_archived/.gitkeep
history/sessions.md
inbox/*.md
